    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(L) In nomine domini nostri Iehsu Christi dei eterni, anno ab incarnathione
                        eius millesimo centesimo optuagesimo quarto, sesto kalendas decembris,
                        indictione secunda. Manifestus sum ego <persName><name ref="Wilielmus"
                                >Guilielmus</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Gherardus">Gerardini</name></persName> quia per hanc cartulam
                        pro remedio anime mee (…) tibi omnipotenti deo et <rs key="#Churches"
                            >ecclesie</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches #Hospitals" ref="#juridical_persons/3206">beati
                            Sancti Iacopi</orgName> sita et composita ad <rs key="#Hospitals"
                            >ospitalem</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Churches #Hospitals" ref="#places/3207"
                            >Tepascii</placeName> (…) dono et trado et concendo (sic) unam pethiam
                        terre que est posita in confinibus <placeName ref="#places/3202"
                            >Montefalconi</placeName> in loco ubi dicitur Comana, iusta a l·aia
                                <persName><name ref="Ribufatus">Ribufati</name></persName> et est
                        tenentes (sic) uno capo cum uno lato in terra dicti Ribufati et alio capo
                        tenet in terra <persName><name ref="Sabatinus">Sabatini</name></persName> et
                        alio lato tenet in terra filio quondam <persName><name ref="Iohannes"
                                >Iohanni</name></persName>. (…) <foreign>Pena</foreign>: in duplum
                        (…) et insuper penam sol. CC. (…) Actum <placeName ref="#places/3210"
                            >Puteo</placeName> in domo eiusdem hospitalis. (…) Signa manuum
                                <persName><name ref="Hubertellus">Ubertelli</name></persName>
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Baldinellus">Baldinelli</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Mancio">Moncini</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Hugolinus">Ugolini</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Mainettus">Manecti</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Widuccius">Guiduci</name></persName> germani et
                        filii quondam <persName><name ref="Bei">Bei</name></persName> rogati testes.
                        (L) Ego <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Gherardus"
                                >Gerardus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> dopni imperatoris Frederigi eis precepto
                        hanc oblathionem in han cartula scripsi. </ab>
                </div>
